![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578252002915-ZRSBZ3A7YL7TM87DM58O/image-asset.jpeg)

Wanna hear a secret? Most of the hosts of the Major Issues Podcast are HUGE wrestling fans? What could wrestling have in common with comic books you ask? Well besides the facts that April bring both Avengers Endgame and Wrestlemania to our door, both mediums actually have alot more in common than you think. Listen to two genuine fans (of both forms of entertainment) talk highs and lows, dynamic costumes, unforgettable cliques and the never-ending fight between good and evil that has been going on since the dawn of time!   
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Don't forget you can always send feedback to us at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

